method.name: GetOrigin
method.abstract: Retrieves the coordinates of the origin of the 3D viewpoint of the annotated view.

method.name: GetSightDirection
method.abstract: Retrieves the components of the sight direction of the 3D viewpoint of the annotated view.

method.name: GetUpDirection
method.abstract: Retrieves the components of the up direction of the 3D viewpoint of the annotated view.

method.name: Update
method.abstract: Updates the annotated view: that is to take into account all modifications which occur since last update.

method.name: BehaviorMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the behavior mode of the annotated view.

method.name: Comment
method.abstract: Returns or sets the comment associated with the annotated view.

method.name: FieldOfView
method.abstract: Returns the field of view associated with the annotated view.

method.name: Marker2Ds
method.abstract: Returns the Marker2D Collection associated with the annotated view.

method.name: ProjectionMode
method.abstract: Returns the projection mode of the annotated view.

method.name: Sound
method.abstract: Returns or sets the path of the sound file associated with the annotated view.

method.name: Zoom
method.abstract: Returns the zoom factor associated with the annotated view.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates an annotated view using the current viewpoint and adds it to the AnnotatedView collection.

method.name: AddFromViewpoint
method.abstract: Creates an annotated view using a given viewpoint and adds it to the AnnotatedView collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns an annotated view using its index or its name from the AnnotatedViews collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes an annotated view from the AnnotatedViews collection.

class.name: DMUDataFlow
class.abstract: Allows the DMU Data Flow Management within the DMU Navigator environment.

method.name: CacheExport
method.abstract: Exports all documents related to the product in a directory.

method.name: CacheImport
method.abstract: Imports in the cache of marked documents in a directory.

method.name: Collapse
method.abstract: Collapse the product by replacing all sub-product by corresponding components.

method.name: ReplaceByCGR
method.abstract: Replaces all components of the product by the corresponding CGR located in a directory.

method.name: SaveAsFrozen
method.abstract: Saves all documents related to the product in a directory.

method.name: AddExplicit
method.abstract: Adds a product to the group.

method.name: CountExplicit
method.abstract: Returns the number of products in the group.

method.name: CountExtract
method.abstract: Returns the number of products which can be extracted from the group.

method.name: CountInvert
method.abstract: Returns the number of terminal node products which cannot be extracted from the group.

method.name: FillSelWithExtract
method.abstract: Fills the selection with all products which can be extracted from the group.

method.name: FillSelWithInvert
method.abstract: Fills the selection with all terminal node products which cannot be extracted from the group.

method.name: ItemExplicit
method.abstract: Returns a product using its index in the group.

method.name: ItemExtract
method.abstract: Returns a product which can be extracted from the group using its index.

method.name: ItemInvert
method.abstract: Returns a terminal node product which cannot be extracted from the group using its index.

method.name: RemoveExplicit
method.abstract: Removes a product from the group using its index.

method.name: ExtractMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the mode for the extraction methods.

class.name: Groups
class.abstract: A collection of all groups currently managed by the application.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates an empty Group and adds it to the Groups Collection.

method.name: AddFromSel
method.abstract: Creates a Group containing all products in the selection and adds it to the Groups Collection.

method.name: AllLeaves
method.abstract: Returns a group which contains all the terminal nodes of the current root product.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a group using its index or its name from the Groups collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a group from the Groups collection.

method.name: AddUrl

method.name: CountObject

method.abstract: Returns an Url which is linked to the Hyperlink using its index.

method.abstract: Removes an Url which is linked to the Hyperlink using its index.

method.abstract: Adds a Hyperlink to the Hyperlinks collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a Hyperlink from the Hyperlinks collection.

class.name: Marker2D

method.name: InsertMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the mode for the Import Applicative Data command (CatSacSettingsEnumNoInsert no import of applicative data, CatSacSettingsEnumAutomatic the import of applicative is automatic, CatSacSettingsEnumUserPrompt the user can select the applicative data to import).

method.name: MarkerAutoUpdate
method.abstract: Returns or sets the activation of the automatic update on product structure modification (TRUE update is done automatically, FALSE update is done manually).

method.name: NumUrlName
method.abstract: Returns or sets the name activation state for Hyperlink (TRUE the hyperlink name is displayed, FALSE the hyperlink name is not displayed).

method.name: PublishAutoLaunchBrowser
method.abstract: Returns or sets the activation state of the automatic launching of the publish browser (TRUE the publish browser is automatically opened, FALSE the publish browser is not automatically opened).
